== 个人生活 ==
2001年席琳成為母親，誕下第一位長子。

2005年[[2005年飓风卡特里娜|卡特琳娜飓风]]袭击美国后，平时很少提及政治话题的席琳在《[[赖瑞金现场|赖瑞金现场]]》节目中抨击了[[乔治·沃克·布什|小布什]]政府在救助灾民时的反应和动员速度简直慢得出奇：“还有那么多人在等待救援。（政府拖沓的作为）在我看来是无法接受的... 为什么（美国政府）往其它国家派飞机瞬间涂炭掉万千生灵就那么容易呢？我们本应（在危难时刻积极）为自己的国家效力。”<ref>{{cite web |title=Canadian Broadcasting Corporation |work=Celine Dion takes swipe at Iraq war; donates $1 m to Katrina victims |url=http://blogs.lasvegasmagazine.com/VegasLuxeLife/our-celine-dion-countdown%E2%80%94just-12-shows-to-go/ |accessdate=14 July 2006 |quote="There's people still there waiting to be rescued. To me that is not acceptable...How can it be so easy to send planes in another country to kill everybody in a second and destroy lives. We need to serve our country." |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071203005953/http://blogs.lasvegasmagazine.com/VegasLuxeLife/our-celine-dion-countdown%E2%80%94just-12-shows-to-go |archivedate=2007年12月3日 }}</ref>访谈过后，她还表示“我在和[[賴瑞金|賴瑞金]]或者其他人上热播节目时，我们就是公众瞩目的焦点，这一点很重要。我当然有自己的观点（想要表达），但我是一个歌手，不是一个政客。”<ref>{{cite book |last=Glatzer |first=Jenna|title=Celine Dion: For Keeps |url=https://archive.org/details/celinedionforkee0000glat |publisher=Andrews McMeel Publishing |year=2005 |isbn=0-7407-5559-5 |quote="When I do interviews with [[拉里·金|Larry King]] or the big TV shows like that, they put you on the spot, which is very difficult. I do have an opinion, but I'm a singer. I'm not a politician."}}</ref>

2010年12月，席琳产下雙胞胎兒子。

2015年3月25日，席琳接受了《早安美國》的獨家訪問，內容談及丈夫René的癌症情況及復出細節，席琳在采訪中不禁流淚談道丈夫必須依靠餵食管幫助進行吞食，自己每天重複地親身照顧癌症復發的丈夫及現年四歲的雙胞胎；席琳另一方面亦宣佈基於丈夫情況已變好，將於今年8月27日重返凱撒官繼續進行駐唱表演。

2016年1月14日，席琳的丈夫雷內於拉斯維加斯的家中因不敵癌症而逝世，終年73歲。席琳的丈夫早於1999年被發現患上癌症，其後治療成功，後在2014年後期發現癌症復發，正面並積極地對抗病情長達一年多，可惜最終依然不敵病情離開世界。雷內的葬禮將會以國葬的形式進行，並且選址在當年1994年與席琳結婚的地方蒙特利爾聖母聖殿（Notre-Dame Basilica）中舉辦。另外相當不幸地，席琳的哥哥丹尼爾亦於雷內離世不到一天的時候也離開了這個世界，亦是因為癌症而帶走丹尼爾的生命。

席琳認識了在荷里活工作的當紅造型師Law Roach，亦因此把她的衣著潮流提升。而於2018年7月，席琳不時把西裝打扮放上社交網站，引起粉絲們的討論<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mings-fashion.com/celine-dion-%E8%A5%BF%E8%A3%9D-fashion-icon-194365/ |title=另類 FASHION ICON︰CÉLINE DION 愛型格西裝成跨界別 DIVA |accessdate=2018-08-09 |archive-date=2018-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180809090855/https://www.mings-fashion.com/celine-dion-%E8%A5%BF%E8%A3%9D-fashion-icon-194365/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 艺术特点 ==

席琳的音乐受流行、摇滚、[[福音音乐|福音]]、[[R&B|R&B]]和[[灵魂乐|灵魂]]等多种风格影响。她的歌词内容则多以“对贫困和饥饿的关注”、“在心灵与精神层面的探寻”以及“对爱与浪漫的诠释”为主题。<ref name="autogenerated23">{{cite web|title=Celine Dion The Colour of My Love|url=http://www.pluggedin.com/music/albums/2002/celinedion-thecolourofmylove.aspx|work=Plugged In|accessdate=27 September 2013|archive-date=2012-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120402231118/http://www.pluggedin.com/music/albums/2002/celinedion-thecolourofmylove.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>"[http://www.pluggedinonline.com/music/music/a0001107.cfm Celine Dion, ''Let's Talk About Love''] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080829161008/http://www.pluggedinonline.com/music/music/a0001107.cfm |date=2008-08-29 }}." ''Plugged in.''. Retrieved 13 September 2007.</ref>在第1个孩子出生后，席琳逐渐增加有关了“母爱”这一新主题的作品数量。<ref name="celebr">[{{Allmusic|class=album|id=r709313|pure_url=yes}} Miracle: A Celebration of New Life]. Allmusic. Retrieved 14 October 2009.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pluggedin.com/music/albums/2002/CelineDion-LetsTalkAboutLove.aspx|title=Celine Dion|work=plugged in.com|publisher=Focus on the Family|year=2009|accessdate=7 January 2010|archive-date=2012-06-02|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/687tYfxwF?url=http://www.pluggedin.com/music/albums/2002/celinedion-letstalkaboutlove.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pluggedin.com/music/albums/2003/CelineDion-OneHeart.aspx|title=Celine Dion-- One Heart|work=plugged in.com|publisher=Focus on the Family|year=2009|accessdate=7 January 2010|archive-date=2012-06-02|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/687tg8Lzp?url=http://www.pluggedin.com/music/albums/2003/CelineDion-OneHeart.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pluggedin.com/music/albums/2002/CelineDion-ANewDayHasCome.aspx|title=A new Day Has Come|work=plugged in.com|publisher=Focus on the Family|year=2009|accessdate=7 January 2010|archive-date=2012-06-02|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/687tgfiiZ?url=http://www.pluggedin.com/music/albums/2002/CelineDion-ANewDayHasCome.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 所受影响 ===
席琳從小至今視不少巨星為偶像，如[[安瑪莉|安瑪莉]]、[[芭芭拉·史翠珊|芭芭拉·史翠珊]]、[[麥可·傑克森|麥可·傑克森]]、[[艾瑞莎·弗蘭克林|艾瑞莎·弗蘭克林]]、[[卡洛爾·金|卡洛爾·金]]及[[比吉斯|比吉斯]]等人，這些人都是曾經相互以不同形式合作過的。另一方面，席琳還欣賞不少前輩，如[[雪兒|雪兒]]、[[蒂娜·特娜|蒂娜·特娜]]及[[伊特·珍|伊特·珍]]等。除此之外，席琳還相當欣賞及相當愛慕於與她同時代的一位女歌手[[惠特尼·休斯頓|惠特尼·休斯頓]]，縱使媒體經常拿兩者作唱功上的比較，但席琳在不少媒體中依然對惠特尼的音樂及聲音讚口不絕。

=== 个人风格 ===

有不少评论批评席琳作品中的煽情元素过于泛滥，甚至使之为流行音乐和灵魂乐的一个退步<small>(retreat)</small>。<ref name="Enc">{{cite web|title=Céline Dion|url=http://www.thecanadianencyclopedia.com/articles/emc/celine-dion|work=The Canadian Encyclopedia|publisher={{link-en|Historica-Dominion|Historica-Dominion}}|accessdate=25 September 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927173706/http://www.thecanadianencyclopedia.com/articles/emc/celine-dion|archivedate=2013年9月27日}}</ref><ref name="autogenerated24">{{cite news|title=findarticles.com|work=The unsinkable Céline Dion — French-Canadian singer — Interview|url=http://www.findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1285/is_3_29/ai_54133689|accessdate=5 December 2005|deadurl=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924050455/http://www.findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1285/is_3_29/ai_54133689|archive-date=2015-09-24}}</ref>《Rolling Stone》杂志的Keith Harris说“席琳（作品中过多）的煽情元素是空洞无物的，让人感觉有些轻浮于表面，而非绝那种（本该有的）腼腆与羞涩之感... (她)处于[[艾瑞莎·弗兰克林|艾瑞莎]] - [[惠特妮·休斯顿|惠特妮]] - [[玛丽亚·凯莉|玛丽亚]]这一系列人物所走过轨迹的最后一环。不但没有发生（与刚才所列轨迹相比的）偏差，席琳还实实在在地成为了流行音乐中特定的一类煽情风格的活广告——（煽情程度）多多益善，天花乱坠都嫌不够，情感越成熟就代表越真实。”<ref>''The New Rolling Stone Album Guide'' 2004. 原文为“[Dion's] sentimentality is bombastic and defiant rather than demure and retiring....[she] stands at the end of the chain of drastic devolution that goes Aretha-Whitney-Mariah. Far from being an aberration, Dion actually stands as a symbol of a certain kind of pop sensibility—bigger is better, too much is never enough, and the riper the emotion the more true.”</ref>与此形成对比的是她的法语作品。她的法语作品比英语作品风格更多变，意味也更深沉（指情感的表达不会停留于表面）。正因为这样，她的法语专辑获得了很高的褒奖。<ref name="autogenerated21">"Celine Dion." ''Newsmakers 1995'', Issue 4. Gale Research, 1995.</ref><ref name=cbcc>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/arts/music/celinedion.html|title=The real Céline: Céline Dion's new French album shows her personal side|publisher=CBC|year=2007|accessdate=7 January 2010|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090331232714/http://cbc.ca/arts/music/celinedion.html|archivedate=2009年3月31日|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

曾有评论因席琳很少参与歌曲制作，认为这样会导致其作品显得泛而不精<ref name="cbcc"/>，缺少来自歌手本人的情感共鸣<ref name="autogenerated21" />。席琳在音乐环境中长大，姐妹都是音乐人。她自己涉猎过钢琴、吉他等多种乐器。在专辑《Falling into You》的录制过程中，她也亲自演奏了[[Fender_Stratocaster|Fender Stratocaster]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/1997/02/23/arts/quebec-s-little-girl-conquering-the-globe.html?pagewanted=all |title=Quebec's Little Girl, Conquering the Globe |work=The New York Times |year=2009 |accessdate=7 January 2010 |first=Anthony |last=Depalma |date=23 February 1997 |archive-date=2015-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723112625/http://www.nytimes.com/1997/02/23/arts/quebec-s-little-girl-conquering-the-globe.html?pagewanted=all |dead-url=no }}</ref>虽然参与得不多，但席琳确实参与过一些歌曲的创作。其中还包括一些写给其他歌手（如Marc Dupre）的歌曲。伴随事业发展，她在各音乐制作环节中的参与度也在逐渐增加。在制作第1张英语专辑时，她表达过一些对制作的不满。如果当时她积极参与到制作过程中去，也许这些到制作后期才出现的争论就可以更早避免。另外，当时她对英语的掌握还未达到很熟悉的程度，在参与交流的时候有些意思可能不能表达到恰到好处。<ref name="autogenerated21" />在第2张专辑《席琳·迪翁》制作时，她对各环节增加了更多的监督，希望能打消掉先前评论家们对上一张专辑中某些不足之处的指指点点。她认为宣布这张专辑的完成又将是一个令人忧虑的选择，因为仍不可能会令其他人100%满意，但已经算是达到自己心目中的标准了。<ref name="autogenerated21" />除在早期几张法语专辑中有亲自写过一些歌曲外，席琳还在《Let's Talk About Love》和《These Are Special Times》中写过几首歌。<ref name="evous.fr">{{cite web|url=http://www.evous.fr/musique/Marc-Dupre-Entre-deux-mondes,11068.html|title=Céline Dion signe le single de Marc Dupré : Ecoutez 'Entre deux mondes'|publisher=Evous.fr|accessdate=27 September 2014|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307182810/http://evous.fr/musique/marc-dupre-entre-deux-mondes,11068.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

席琳经常会在各种媒体节目中被拿出来说事，比如开一些小的玩笑<ref>See, e.g., {{link-en|Joel Selvin|Joel Selvin}}, [http://www.sfgate.com/music/article/Celine-Dion-in-full-force-at-HP-Pavilion-3170389.php "Celine Dion in full force at HP Pavilion"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sfgate.com/music/article/Celine-Dion-in-full-force-at-HP-Pavilion-3170389.php |date=20170821084224 }}, ''[[San_Francisco_Chronicle|San Francisco Chronicle]]'', 23 February 2009, E2. In this rather hostile review, Selvin wrote: "You want cheese? She is a {{link-en|Velveeta|Velveeta}} volcano."</ref>或者被人故意模仿取乐。搞怪模仿的对象多是她的口音和各种习惯性手势。其中对她的搞怪频率比较高的节目有《MADtv》、《[[周六夜现场|周六夜现场]]》、《[[南方公园|南方公园]]》、《Royal Canadian Air Farce》和《This Hour Has 22 Minutes》等。不过，席琳曾表示自己对此并不在意，而且觉得能有不少人乐意花时间去模仿自己是一件足以津津乐道的事情。<ref name="vh1">{{cite web | title=VH1 | work=Céline Dion: Let's Talk About Success: The Singer Explains Her Career High-Points | url=http://www.vh1.com/artists/interview/1453531/04222002/dion_celine.jhtml | accessdate=19 December 2005 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050330094606/http://www.vh1.com/artists/interview/1453531/04222002/dion_celine.jhtml | archivedate=2005年3月30日 }}</ref>她还邀请过曾经在《周六夜现场》中模仿过自己的Ana Gasteyer在自己的纽约演唱会上现场表演。2015年，在第55届《[[瑞典旋律节|瑞典旋律节]]》中，主持人[[桑娜·尼尔森|桑娜·尼尔森]]就模仿席琳·迪翁唱了一段她当年夺冠的歌曲《Ne partez pas sans moi》。

=== 声音特色 ===
席琳的声音被视为流行音乐界最有影响力的声音之一<ref name= Enc/><ref name="autogenerated21" /><ref>Andersson, Eric. "Who Inspired the Idols?" ''Us''. 12 March 2007. p. 104</ref>。美國版[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]（Time Magazine）於1996年稱席琳為流行天后（The Divas of Pop）並獨佔雜誌封面<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://eil.com/shop/moreinfo.asp?catalogid=290340 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2019-05-05 |archive-date=2019-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190519104240/https://eil.com/shop/moreinfo.asp?catalogid=290340 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Linda Lister在《Divafication: The Deification of Modern Female Pop Stars》中将对90年代唱片业有巨大影响的席琳、[[惠特尼·休斯顿|惠特尼·休斯顿]]和[[玛丽亚·凯莉|玛丽亚·凯莉]]等女艺人称为“流行乐女王”<small>(Queen of Pop)</small>。<ref name= diva>"If Ella Fitzgerald is the queen of jazz, Billie Holiday first lady of the blues, and Aretha Franklin the queen of soul, then who is the queen of pop? In the 1990s, it would seem to be a three-way tie between Whitney Houston, Mariah Carey, and Celine Dion. Certainly all three have their devotees and detractors, but their presence has been inescapable." in {{Cite news | last1= Lister | first1=Linda | title=Divafication: The Deification of Modern Female Pop Stars| newspaper=Popular Music and Society | volume=25|issue=3/4| page=1| year= 2001|issn=03007766 | postscript= <!-- Bot inserted parameter. Either remove it; or change its value to "." for the cite to end in a ".", as necessary. -->}}</ref>《Blender》杂志曾将席琳列为“22位最伟大的歌手”<small>(22 Greatest Voices in Music)</small>中的第9名。而《Cove》杂志则将她列在“100位杰出流行歌唱艺人”<small>(The 100 Outstanding Pop Vocalists)</small>中的第5名。<ref name=cove>{{cite web| title=Cove Magazine| work=The 100 Outstanding Pop Vocalists| url=http://covemagazine.com/100vocalists.html| accessdate=29 August 2006| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060716122547/http://www.covemagazine.com/100vocalists.html| archivedate=2006年7月16日}}</ref><ref name=mtv22ist>{{cite web| title= MTV's 22 Greatest Voices in Music| work= mtv's 22| url= http://www.listology.com/list/mtvs-22-greatest-voices-music| accessdate= 15 November 2007| archive-date= 2011-12-21| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20111221110955/http://www.listology.com/list/mtvs-22-greatest-voices-music| dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amiannoying.com/(S(ooqu0o45hssi4szgpvg5lb55))/collection.aspx?collection=534|title=22 Greatest Voices in Music|publisher=Amiannoying.com|accessdate=27 September 2014|archive-date=2019-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626233913/http://www.amiannoying.com/(S(242anlvaugq1jcixuvn5wnbv))/collection.aspx?collection=534|dead-url=no}}</ref>人们常拿席琳的歌唱风格与玛丽亚·凯莉及惠特尼·休斯顿作比较，也常拿席琳的嗓音与她本人的偶像[[芭芭拉·史翠珊|芭芭拉·史翠珊]]作比较。<ref>{{cite news |last=Depalma |first=Anthony |url=http://www.nytimes.com/1997/02/23/arts/quebec-s-little-girl-conquering-the-globe.html?pagewanted=all |title=POP/JAZZ V Quebec's Little Girl, Conquering the Globe |location=Quebec Province (Canada) |work=The New York Times |date=23 February 1997 |accessdate=30 June 2010 |archive-date=2015-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723112625/http://www.nytimes.com/1997/02/23/arts/quebec-s-little-girl-conquering-the-globe.html?pagewanted=all |dead-url=no }}</ref>

不少资料认为，席琳拥有横跨5个[[八度|八度]]的[[音域|音域]]。<!--以下这几项来源中确实有明确写出其音域是“FIVE OCTAVES”。--><ref>{{cite web|url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/music/news/2007-11-11-celine-dion_N.htm|title=Celine Dion is 'Taking Chances' with her latest show stopper|publisher=Usatoday30.usatoday.com|accessdate=27 September 2014|archive-date=2015-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151020212331/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/music/news/2007-11-11-celine-dion_N.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/1997/02/23/arts/quebec-s-little-girl-conquering-the-globe.html?pagewanted=all Quebec's Little Girl, Conquering the Globe] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1997/02/23/arts/quebec-s-little-girl-conquering-the-globe.html?pagewanted=all |date=20150723112625 }} ''New York Times''. Retrieved 26 December 2009.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=PBPB&p_theme=pbpb&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EAF3F953584E833&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|title=People to Watch|publisher=Nl.newsbank.com|accessdate=27 September 2014|archive-date=2015-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017065230/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=PBPB&p_theme=pbpb&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EAF3F953584E833&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|dead-url=no}}</ref>但可以肯定的是，席琳至少拥有从[[B_(音名)|B2]]到[[E_(音名)|Eb6]]共跨越3个八度的音域。<!--The sources state 5 octaves, now go back. Watch her video of her vocal range going from B2 ~ Eb6, B2 being the B an octave below the B right beside middle C, aka C4. Eb6 is an Eb two octaves above middle C. Let's do the math. B2 to B3, 1 octave, to B4, 2 octaves, to B5, 3 octaves. Two semitones up, Eb6. Now, if you can find Celine hitting a B7, or a B6 and a B1, then sure, you can say she has 5 octaves. Sources are nice, but facts are too. The citations here, if you don't consider them reliable, then what is reliable? Magazines and news that state random facts without any proof behind it? I think videos showing her real range is very reputable and pretty factual.--><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bdwf8IuKTxI|title=Celine Dion V Live Vocal Range (B2 V Eb6) 3.2 Octaves|publisher=youtube.com|accessdate=3 October 2014|archive-date=2017-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409160953/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bdwf8IuKTxI|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jsC1WYJoLOI|title=Celine Dion's Live Vocal Range: B2-C#6 (3.4 Octaves)|publisher=youtube.com|accessdate=3 October 2014|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518172430/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jsC1WYJoLOI|dead-url=no}}</ref>席琳曾自认为是一个[[次女高音|次女高音]]<small>(mezzo-soprano)</small>。<ref name="Cyberpresse.ca">{{cite web |url=http://www.lapresse.ca/arts/musique/200809/08/01-658078-celine-dion-chante-de-lopera-pour-kent-nagano.php |title=Alain de Repentigny : Celine Dion chante de l'opera pour Kent Nagano | Musique |publisher=Cyberpresse.ca |accessdate=30 June 2010 |archive-date=2018-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180103025338/http://www.lapresse.ca/arts/musique/200809/08/01-658078-celine-dion-chante-de-lopera-pour-kent-nagano.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>不过，古典的音域分类方式如何应用于新形势的音乐演唱本身就是一个存在一些争议的问题。<ref>Peckham, Anne (2005). ''Vocal workouts for the contemporary singer.'' Boston: Berklee Press. pp. 117. ISBN 978-0-87639-047-4.</ref>音乐[[指挥家|指挥家]][[长野健|长野健]]曾经表示自己很想听一听席琳唱歌剧是什么效果。他听完席琳演唱《[[卡门|卡门]]》中的2段独唱后，未对音域进行详细分类，只是评论说“你唱的是[[女高音|女高音]]”。<ref name="Cyberpresse.ca"/>人们用“细而略带鼻音”<small>(thin, slightly nasal)</small><ref name="NYTIS">{{cite news |last=Holden |first=Stephen |url=http://www.nytimes.com/1994/03/02/arts/review-pop-the-international-sound-of-celine-dion.html?pagewanted=1 |title=Review/Pop – The International Sound of Celine Dion – Review |work=The New York Times |date=2 March 1994 |accessdate=30 June 2010 |archive-date=2015-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723114235/http://www.nytimes.com/1994/03/02/arts/review-pop-the-international-sound-of-celine-dion.html?pagewanted=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、带有“急促的稍低音”<small>(a raspy lower register)</small>和“玻璃铃铛一样清脆的高调”<small>(bell glass-like high notes)</small><ref>{{cite news |last=Hazera |first=Hélène |url=http://www.liberation.fr/culture/1999/06/21/dion-dans-les-grandes-largeurssamedi-et-dimanche-l-idole-canadienne-a-rempli-le-stade-de-france_275750 |title=Dion dans les grandes largeurs : Samedi et dimanche, l'idole canadienne a rempli le Stade de France |work=Libération |date=21 June 1999 |accessdate=16 March 2011 |archive-date=2015-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722140904/http://www.liberation.fr/culture/1999/06/21/dion-dans-les-grandes-largeurssamedi-et-dimanche-l-idole-canadienne-a-rempli-le-stade-de-france_275750 |dead-url=no }}</ref>等词描述她的音质。

席琳的唱功常受到评论褒奖。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=qFM1AAAAIBAJ&sjid=YyUMAAAAIBAJ&pg=3124,21671065&dq=celine+dion+virtuosity&hl=en|title=Celine Dion Takes Chances in Latest Album|publisher=News.google.com|accessdate=27 September 2014|archive-date=2015-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907202606/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=qFM1AAAAIBAJ&sjid=YyUMAAAAIBAJ&pg=3124,21671065&dq=celine+dion+virtuosity&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>《The Buffalo News》的Jim Santella曾描述“席琳·迪翁的声音像铁拳藏在鹅绒手套中一般（刚柔相济），其力量隐蔽在柔滑的颤音之中，透露出其在唱功方面的强大造诣。”<ref name="BuffaloT">{{Cite news |last=Santella |first=Jim |url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=BN&p_theme=bn&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EAF9C3898C21652&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM |title=The Diva Debate Queen Celine |work=The Buffalo News |date=19 September 1999 |accessdate=5 January 2013 |quote="...like an iron fist in a velvet glove, the power of Celine Dion's voice is cloaked in a silky vibrato that betrays the intensity of her vocal commitment." |archive-date=2018-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181215133422/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=BN&p_theme=bn&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EAF9C3898C21652&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM |dead-url=no }}</ref>《The Buffalo News》的另一评论员Jeff Miers说：“她的声音超越到了人类的极致。她（能）全力冲上高音，同时自如地收发颤音，还能完美地把握好音调（的微妙变化）。整个过程就像是她在干净利落地将一束玉米剥皮。”<ref name="BuffaloT2">{{Cite news|last=Miers|first=Jeff|url=http://www.redorbit.com/news/entertainment/1544288/a_long_strange_trip_with_celine/|title=A Long, Strange Trip with Celine|work=The Buffalo News|date=4 September 2008|accessdate=5 January 2013|quote="Her singing voice is absolutely extra-human. She hits notes in full voice, with a controlled vibrato and an incredible conception of pitch, like she's shucking an ear of corn..."|archive-date=2015-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150114212425/http://www.redorbit.com/news/entertainment/1544288/a_long_strange_trip_with_celine/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《The New York Times》编辑Stephen Holden说席琳的“各方面功夫都很齐全。她可以对各种{{link-en|花唱|melismas}}技巧信手拈来，演绎出摄人心魄的歌唱表现，能在稳住音调细微波动的同时长时间地飚出高音。而在二人合唱中... 能看出她是个(配合程度)很靠得住的和声。（即指她的配合水平高，与别人总能很快默契配合。）”<ref name="NYTIS"/><ref>原文为“a good-sized arsenal of technical skills. She can deliver tricky melismas, produce expressive vocal catches and sustain long notes without the tiniest wavering of pitch. And as her duets [...] have shown, she is a reliable harmony voice.”</ref>[[长野健|长野健]]说“(席琳是一个)有敏锐听觉、良好资质以及完美境界的音乐人，令人羡慕嫉妒”。<ref name="Cyberpresse.ca"/><ref>原文为“a musician who has a good ear, a refinement, and a degree of perfection that is enviable.”</ref>《时代》编辑Charles Alexander说“(她的)声音能从轻声的低语毫不费力地滑移到极高的音调，仿佛一种融力量感与优雅于一体的甜蜜的乐笛声。”<ref name="autogenerated18"/><ref>原文为“[Her] voice glides effortlessly from deep whispers to dead-on high notes, a sweet siren that combines force with grace.”</ref><ref>引文中的“siren”本指[[希腊神话|希腊神话]]中的[[塞壬|塞壬]]，是一种歌声有很强诱惑力的海妖。</ref>

对于经常演唱的法语曲目，席琳将自己的唱腔装饰得更精致和更具表现力，带上了一层“更富有温柔和亲密感”<small>(more tender and intimate)</small>的抒情色彩。<ref name="Denise Bombardier 2009, page 179">Denise Bombardier, L'enigmatique Celine Dion, Albin Michel XO editions, 2009, page 179.</ref>与席琳有过密切合作的法国[[唱作人|唱作人]]Luc Plamondon曾称席琳吸纳了法国、魁北克、美国三地的歌谣演唱风格。<ref name="Denise Bombardier 2009, page 179"/>她的同名专辑上写着“记住这个名字，因为这个声音将使你永久无法忘怀”<small>(Remember the name because you'll never forget the voice)</small>。

===個人影響力===

音樂製作人及前任[[美國偶像|美國偶像]]裁判之一[[蘭道爾·大流士·蘭迪·傑克遜|蘭道爾·大流士·蘭迪·傑克遜]]說："[[席琳·迪翁|席琳·迪翁]]、[[惠特尼·休斯頓|惠特尼·休斯頓]]及[[瑪麗亞·凱莉|瑪麗亞·凱莉]]是在黃金時代裡擁有最棒聲音的歌手，很多女歌手都很推祟。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a367273/american-idol-randy-jackson-whitney-houston-was-voice-of-generation.html#~pbMTa2Zj1tLUz1 |title='American Idol' Randy Jackson: Whitney Houston was voice of generation |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2015-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518062131/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a367273/american-idol-randy-jackson-whitney-houston-was-voice-of-generation.html#~pbMTa2Zj1tLUz1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>"
文化評論家卡爾·威爾遜指出，席琳的知名度與影響力是依然流存，這些東西都可以在[[美國偶像|美國偶像]]裡一一體現。在過去十年的大規模音樂現象下，席琳依然非常札實地成為年輕人采樣成為歌手的對象。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://flavorwire.com/90128/why-celine-dion-will-always-be-popular-at-least-while-youre-alive |title=Why Celine Dion Will Always Be Popular — At Least While You’re Alive |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2017-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171027024639/http://flavorwire.com/90128/why-celine-dion-will-always-be-popular-at-least-while-youre-alive |dead-url=no }}</ref>

現代很多歌手都深受席琳影響或視她為偶像，如[[蕾哈娜|蕾哈娜]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.artistdirect.com/nad/news/article/0,,3655378,00.html |title="ARTISTdirect's Exclusive Interview With Rihanna! |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2018-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180310051122/http://www.artistdirect.com/nad/news/article/0,,3655378,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[布蘭妮·斯皮爾斯|布蘭妮·斯皮爾斯]]、[[芮塔·歐拉|芮塔·歐拉]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/bizarre/4314437/RIP-singer-Rita-Ora-has-revealed-she-is-a-massive-fan-of-Celine-Dion.html |title=R.I.P. singer Rita Ora has revealed she is a massive fan of Celine Dion {{!}} The Sun {{!}}Showbiz{{!}}Bizarre |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2014-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221194333/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/bizarre/4314437/RIP-singer-Rita-Ora-has-revealed-she-is-a-massive-fan-of-Celine-Dion.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[克莉絲汀·阿奎萊拉|克莉絲汀·阿奎萊拉]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UoINJdqVsdw |title=Christina Aguilera talks about Celine Dion |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2017-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170408141531/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UoINJdqVsdw |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[喬許·葛洛班|喬許·葛洛班]]<ref>[http://www.grobanarchives.com/interviews/int070809b.html Josh Groban Defends Celine Dion] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140409075232/http://www.grobanarchives.com/interviews/int070809b.html |date=2014-04-09 }}</ref>、[[愛黛兒|愛黛兒]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2008/jan/27/popandrock.britawards2008 |title=Mad about the girl |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2015-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150711182439/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2008/jan/27/popandrock.britawards2008 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[女神卡卡|女神卡卡]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZpwPhh91w2Q |title=存档副本 |access-date=2019-04-14 |archive-date=2022-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122083517/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZpwPhh91w2Q }}</ref>、[[黛兒塔|黛兒塔]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.perthnow.com.au/entertainment/delta-teams-up-with-idol-celine/story-e6frg3i3-1111114635115 |title=Delta Goodrem teams up with her idol Celine Dion |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2013-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131027084335/http://www.perthnow.com.au/entertainment/delta-teams-up-with-idol-celine/story-e6frg3i3-1111114635115 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[里歐娜·路易斯|里歐娜·路易斯]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hub.contactmusic.com/the-x-factor/news/lewis-to-meet-pop-idol-celine-dion_1048112 |title=Lewis To Meet Pop Idol Celine Dion |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2015-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518060612/http://hub.contactmusic.com/the-x-factor/news/lewis-to-meet-pop-idol-celine-dion_1048112 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[亞莉安娜·格蘭德|亞莉安娜·格蘭德]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=llAd0xkYr74 |title=Ariana Grande talking about celine dion |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2017-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409170227/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=llAd0xkYr74 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[法蘭克海洋|法蘭克海洋]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rap-up.com/2012/03/23/frank-ocean-gets-up-close-in-i-d-magazine/ |title=FRANK OCEAN GETS UP CLOSE IN I-D MAGAZINE |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2015-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150118030552/http://www.rap-up.com/2012/03/23/frank-ocean-gets-up-close-in-i-d-magazine/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[夏芮絲|夏芮絲]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jZyVxwDV4Y0 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2015-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150529020422/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jZyVxwDV4Y0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[泰勒絲|泰勒絲]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SQSjsbf8ufk |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2014-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140522153510/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SQSjsbf8ufk |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[珍妮佛·哈德森|珍妮佛·哈德森]]、[[喬安娜·李文絲奇|喬安娜·李文絲奇]]、[[潔西_J|潔西 J]]、[[裘汀·史芭克絲|裘汀·史芭克絲]]、[[凡妮莎·哈金斯|凡妮莎·哈金斯]]、[[費絲·希爾|費絲·希爾]]、[[凱蒂·佩芮|凱蒂·佩芮]]、[[凱莉·克萊森|凱莉·克萊森]]及[[蘿拉·菲比安|蘿拉·菲比安]]等人。在蘿拉的其中一張專輯Toutes les femmes en moi中，她展現了她極愛幕席琳的一面，專輯裡其中一段文字寫下："我會一直一直注意著你的音樂，欣賞著你對音樂的熱情，嘗試跟你一樣把歌曲唱得有它的色彩和和諧。"

除了不少人把席琳當成偶像外，很多歌手亦對席琳的聲音表示欣賞及對席琳的唱功表示讚嘆，如[[卡洛爾·金|卡洛爾·金]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nAnYYNFH8p8 |title=Celine Dion - The Reason (The Sessions) |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2019-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190614001246/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nAnYYNFH8p8 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[碧昂絲·諾利斯|碧昂絲·諾利斯]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/news/a482368/beyonce-got-parenting-tip-from-celine-dion-i-use-a-mommy-voice.html |title=Beyoncé got parenting tip from Celine Dion: 'I use a mommy voice' |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2015-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017065229/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/news/a482368/beyonce-got-parenting-tip-from-celine-dion-i-use-a-mommy-voice.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[艾爾頓·強|艾爾頓·強]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s0LYcewRn4E |title=Celine Dion & Elton John - H.E.A.R.T. Concert (Entertainment Tonight 21-02-2006) |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2017-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170408102133/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s0LYcewRn4E |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[妮可·舒辛格|妮可·舒辛格]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/NicoleScherzy/status/399659802487689216 |title="Twitter / NicoleScherzy: Such an honour to meet" |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2016-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412043937/https://twitter.com/nicolescherzy/status/399659802487689216 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[萊諾·李奇|萊諾·李奇]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q3Aoz9IXObg |title=存档副本 |access-date=2019-04-14 |archive-date=2022-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122092502/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q3Aoz9IXObg }}</ref>、[[酷玩樂團|酷玩樂團]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.irishexaminer.com/breakingnews/ireland/cwcweyqlgbcw/ |title=Martin eyes Coldplay duet with Dion |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2015-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017065229/http://www.irishexaminer.com/breakingnews/ireland/cwcweyqlgbcw/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[卡洛斯·山塔那|卡洛斯·山塔那]]<ref>[http://www.canada.com/topics/entertainment/story.html?id=a300bad2-4877-481e-b591-7c0491922654 Legendary Santana lets his guitar fly solo] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140314195854/http://www.canada.com/topics/entertainment/story.html?id=a300bad2-4877-481e-b591-7c0491922654 |date=2014-03-14 }}</ref>、[[賈斯汀|賈斯汀]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nerienlouper.fr/44957-indiscretions-justin-bieber-en-duo-avec-celine-dion-pour-believe/ |title=Indiscrétions : Justin Bieber en duo avec Céline Dion pour Believe? |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2015-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017065229/http://www.nerienlouper.fr/44957-indiscretions-justin-bieber-en-duo-avec-celine-dion-pour-believe/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[雪兒|雪兒]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-2gUi8wjMS0 |title=Cher talks about Celine Dion's voice |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2015-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017065229/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-2gUi8wjMS0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[仙妮亞·唐恩|仙妮亞·唐恩]]<ref>[http://www.celinedion.com/ca/node/166170 Shania Twain in the footsteps of Celine Dion in Las Vegas] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419044157/http://www.celinedion.com/ca/node/166170 |date=2014-04-19 }}</ref>、[[讓-雅克·高德曼|讓-雅克·高德曼]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d37XYawD-pc |title=Céline Dion et Jean-Jacques Goldman "S'il suffisait d'aimer" - Archive INA |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2019-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605120222/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d37XYawD-pc |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[尼歐_(歌手)|尼歐 (歌手)]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/1552164/ne-yo-teams-with-celine-dion-for-duet-it-definitely-made-me |title=Ne-Yo Teams With Celine Dion for Duet: 'It Definitely Made Me Question My Vocal Ability' |accessdate=2015-05-05 |archive-date=2015-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150611002529/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/1552164/ne-yo-teams-with-celine-dion-for-duet-it-definitely-made-me |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[芭芭拉·史翠珊|芭芭拉·史翠珊]]、[[盧奇亞諾·帕華洛帝|盧奇亞諾·帕華洛帝]]、[[比吉斯|比吉斯]]、[[喬治·馬丁|喬治·馬丁]]等人。

在法語文化層面上，席琳一直致力於將法語音樂帶到世界各地進行演唱，令世界各地不同的人都能接觸法語音樂，其中席琳於1995年的一張專輯《他們》（D'eux）是目前全球最高銷量的法語專輯，在一些非法語國家如英國、日本、波蘭、希臘等市場取下非預期性的成功，其中英國更拿下金唱片認證的創先河的紀錄。於2008年5月22日，席琳在巴黎接受法國總統[[薩科齊|薩科齊]]親自頒發法國最高榮耀的[[法國榮譽軍團勳章|法國榮譽軍團勳章]]<ref>[http://www.canada.com/vancouversun/news/story.html?id=10c4a258-589c-4aae-a907-7610b3323520 Dion receives French Legion of Honour] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013115046/http://www.canada.com/vancouversun/news/story.html?id=10c4a258-589c-4aae-a907-7610b3323520 |date=2013-10-13 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.liberation.fr/actualite/2008/05/22/celine-dion-decoree-de-la-legion-d-honneur-par-nicolas-sarkozy_15704 |title=Celine Dion decoree de la Legion d'honneur par Nicolas Sarkozy |accessdate=2015-02-15 |archive-date=2017-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222052234/http://www.liberation.fr/actualite/2008/05/22/celine-dion-decoree-de-la-legion-d-honneur-par-nicolas-sarkozy_15704 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，勳章認證席琳在宣傳法語文化上有著極高的推動力及影響力。除了後期把法語文化推動到世界各地外，席琳已經早於1996年接受了法國政府文化部頒下來的[[法蘭西藝術與文學勳章|法蘭西藝術與文學勳章]]中的騎士勳章以表揚席琳在文學界或藝術界是具有傑出貢獻的人物<ref>[http://www.celinedion.com/ca/awards The Journey So Far] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140109154008/http://www.celinedion.com/ca/awards |date=2014-01-09 }}</ref>。

在加拿大音樂行業層面上，於1999年，席琳成為了繼[[布萊恩·亞當斯|布萊恩·亞當斯]]及[[安瑪莉|安瑪莉]]後第三位歌手進駐加拿大廣播名人堂（Canadian Broadcast Hall of Fame）以認證席琳對加拿大音樂行業的高度貢獻<ref>[http://www.broadcasting-history.ca/index3.html?url=http%3A//www.broadcasting-history.ca/personalities/personalities.php%3Fid%3D206 Member of CAB Hall of Fame] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402091432/http://www.broadcasting-history.ca/index3.html?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.broadcasting-history.ca%2Fpersonalities%2Fpersonalities.php%3Fid%3D206 |date=2015-04-02 }}</ref>。2013年7月26日，席琳亦在加拿大接受了[[加拿大總督|加拿大總督]]頒發的[[加拿大勳章|加拿大勳章]]<ref>[http://www.celinedion.com/ca/news/order-canada-investiture-celine-and-ren%C3%A9 Order Of Canada Investiture For Celine and Rene] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130729030010/http://www.celinedion.com/ca/news/order-canada-investiture-celine-and-ren%C3%A9 |date=2013-07-29 }}</ref>，此國家級獎項以認證席琳在加拿大國家層面上有著極高的影響力。同年也在加拿大拿下加拿大星光大道（Canada's Walk of Fame）中屬於自己的星星。

美國VH1將席琳位列於《史上最偉大流行文化偶像前200名》（200 Greatest Pop Culture Icons of All Time）排行榜中的第64名，歌手排名中的第12名<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.amiannoying.com/(S(ye5qhdv4o1ay13t5zgcpxwq4))/collection.aspx?collection=1412 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2019-03-03 |archive-date=2020-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200210091534/http://www.amiannoying.com/(S(yeisq3l5ykyyjm0rt23llogu))/collection.aspx?collection=1412 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。於2003年，VH1也把席琳評為《影片時代最佳50大女性》（50 Greatest Women of the Video Era）中的第10名<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20110629061423/http://www.vh1.com/shows/the_greatest/episode.jhtml?episodeID=66355</ref>。美國搖滾名人堂也將席琳其中之一的專輯《戀上你》（Falling Into You）列於其《史上最權威的200張專輯》（The Definitive 200 Albums）排名榜中的第97名<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20070309200014/http://definitive200.com/200_list.php</ref>。2004年，席琳也在美國荷里活星光大道（Hollywood Walk of Fame）以歌手身份拿下屬於自己的星星。

